OL,7,FThe Business and Trade Committee has
OL,8,Fcalled for the Post Office to be
OL,9,Fcompletely removed from overseeing
OL,10,Fcompensation schemes
OL,12,FMPs on a parliamentary committee say
OL,13,Fthe Post Office is "not fit" to handle
OL,14,Fcompensation schemes for victims of
OL,15,Fthe scandal.
OL,17,FThe Business and Trade Committee has
OL,18,Fcalled for the Post Office to be
OL,19,Fcompletely removed from overseeing
OL,20,Fcompensation schemes, in a report
OL,21,Freleased on Thursday.
