OL,7,FThe report concluded the company is
OL,8,F"not fit for purpose to administer any
OL,9,Fof the schemes of redress required to
OL,10,Fmake amends for one of the biggest
OL,11,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,12,Fhistory".
OL,14,FThe committee has now demanded an
OL,15,Findependent body be established to
OL,16,Fhelp victims "through every stage of
OL,17,Ftheir compensation claims" `
OL,18,Fdescribing the current redress process
OL,19,Fas an "abject failure".
