OL,7,FThe report also calls for legally
OL,8,Fbinding deadlines for when redress
OL,9,Fshould be delivered to affected sub-
OL,10,Fpostmasters in order to stop
OL,11,F"unacceptable delays" ` an idea
OL,12,Fsuggested by lead campaigner Alan
OL,13,FBates during his evidence to MPs last
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,16,FChairman of the committee, Liam Byrne,
OL,17,Flabelled it a "national disgrace" that
OL,18,F"only #1 in #5 of the budget for
OL,19,Fcompensation has been issued" to sub-
OL,20,Fpostmasters.
