OL,7,FThe report also recommends removing a
OL,8,Fcap on victims' legal expenses and the
OL,9,Fintroduction of a standardised set of
OL,10,Ftariffs to help estimate what they are
OL,11,Fentitled to.
OL,13,FMr Byrne said: "Justice delayed is
OL,14,Fjustice denied. And bluntly justice
OL,15,Fhas been denied to our innocent sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters for far too long.
OL,18,F"It's high time for the circus of
OL,19,Frecent weeks to end and for cheques to
OL,20,Fstart landing on the doormats of
OL,21,Finnocent victims.
