OL,7,F"We now know the Post Office knew of
OL,8,Fproblems 20 years ago."
OL,10,FMr Bryne also criticised the public
OL,11,Fspat between the current Post Office
OL,12,Fboss and the former chairman.
OL,14,FAfter former chairman Henry Staunton -
OL,15,Fwho had been - shocked MPs when he
OL,16,Frevealed that current CEO Nick Read
OL,17,Fwas also under investigation, citing
OL,18,Fan 80-page HR report about him.
